I"b<h2 id="lara系统安装">Lara系统安装</h2>
<ol>
  <li>下载源码
    <blockquote>
      <p>引用文本 Blockquotes
在命令行界面输入 git clone https://github.com/zhangfangsong/Lara.git下载源码，</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>国内网速慢的同学可以用码云地址：https://gitee.com/zfs/Lara.git</p>

<p>wwwroot root$ git clone https://github.com/zhangfangsong/Lara.git
Initialized empty Git repository in /home/wwwroot/Lara/.git/
remote: Counting objects: 5540, done.
remote: Compressing objects: 100% (4025/4025), done.
